e=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://desmistificando.com.br/como-corrigir-dados-no-cnis/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Desmistificando o Direito</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+2</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">ABL Advogados</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+2</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1085\" data-end=\"1129\">\n<p data-start=\"1088\" data-end=\"1129\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">envio dos documentos digitalmente por meio do Meu INSS</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1130\" data-end=\"1212\">\n<p data-start=\"1133\" data-end=\"1212\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">acompanhamento pelo sistema e resposta, dentro do prazo estimado de até 30 dias — embora, em alguns casos, esse prazo se estenda</span> <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://exame.com/brasil/guia-do-cidadao/como-corrigir-o-cnis-pela-internet-para-se-aposentar/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">ssantos.adv.br</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+13</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Exame</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+13</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Serviços e Informações do Brasil</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+13</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 data-start=\"1214\" data-end=\"1260\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"qual_o_impacto_pratico_de_corrigir_o_CNIS\"></span>qual o impacto prático de corrigir o CNIS<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n<p data-start=\"1261\" data-end=\"1300\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">A correção pode resultar em aumento expressivo do benefício e no reconhecimento de tempo faltante ou salários desconsiderados. Por exemplo, incluir vínculo e remuneração de mais um ano pode elevar a média contributiva em centenas ou milhares de reais — conferindo reajuste permanente e retroativo.</span></p>\n<h2 data-start=\"1302\" data-end=\"1337\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"quando_recorrer_a_via_judicial\"></span>quando recorrer à via judicial<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n<p data-start=\"1338\" data-end=\"1377\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Se o INSS negar o acerto ou demorar demais, cabe ação judicial, com pedido liminar, especialmente quando a aposentadoria está em curso ou a urgência é evidente (idade avançada, auxílio ativo, etc.). O advogado previdenciário pode instruir processo apresentando CTPS, contracheques, cálculos e extratos, fortalecendo sua tese judicial de direito líquido e certo.</span></p>\n<h2 data-start=\"1379\" data-end=\"1440\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"prazo_para_revisao_apos_beneficio_concedido_decadencia\"></span>prazo para revisão após benefício concedido (decadência)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n<p data-start=\"1441\" data-end=\"1561\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">O segurado tem até 10 anos após o primeiro pagamento do benefício para solicitar revisão, conforme prazo decadencial da Lei 8.213/91</span> <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://www.rogeriograndino.com.br/e-possivel-revisar-o-valor-da-aposentadoria-apos-a-concessao?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Lemos de Miranda</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+4</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">rogeriograndino.com.br</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+4</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">lucastubino.adv.br</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+4</span></span></span></a></span></span><span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://lucastubino.adv.br/revisao-da-aposentadoria-por-erros-no-salario/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">lucastubino.adv.br</span></span></span></a></span></span>. <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Após esse prazo, ações costumam ser indeferidas— salvo situações excepcionais como erro grave do INSS.</span></p>\n<h2 data-start=\"1563\" data-end=\"1609\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"correcao_vs_revisao_entenda_a_diferenca\"></span>correção vs. revisão: entenda a diferença<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n<p data-start=\"1610\" data-end=\"1649\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Acerto do CNIS é porque o cadastro estava incorreto — etapa antecede ou fundamenta qualquer benefício. Já revisão é pedido para recálculo de benefício já concedido — ajusta valor ou tempo reconhecido com base nos dados corrigidos.</span></p>\n<h2 data-start=\"1651\" data-end=\"1712\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tabela_%E2%80%93_comparacao_de_situacao_antes_e_depois_da_correcao\"></span>tabela – comparação de situação antes e depois da correção<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n<div class=\"_tableContainer_1rjym_1\">\n<div class=\"_tableWrapper_1rjym_13 group flex w-fit flex-col-reverse\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<table class=\"w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)\" data-start=\"1714\" data-end=\"2286\">\n<thead data-start=\"1714\" data-end=\"1817\">\n<tr data-start=\"1714\" data-end=\"1817\">\n<th data-start=\"1714\" data-end=\"1754\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Situação</th>\n<th data-start=\"1754\" data-end=\"1778\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Tempo de contribuição</th>\n<th data-start=\"1778\" data-end=\"1795\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Média salarial</th>\n<th data-start=\"1795\" data-end=\"1817\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Benefício estimado</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody data-start=\"1923\" data-end=\"2286\">\n<tr data-start=\"1923\" data-end=\"2114\">\n<td data-start=\"1923\" data-end=\"1987\" data-col-size=\"sm\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">CNIS sem acerto</span></td>\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"1987\" data-end=\"2012\">28 anos</td>\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"2012\" data-end=\"2060\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">R$ 2.000</span></td>\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"2060\" data-end=\"2114\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">R$ 1.600</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr data-start=\"2115\" data-end=\"2286\">\n<td data-start=\"2115\" data-end=\"2159\" data-col-size=\"sm\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">CNIS revisado com vínculo faltante</span></td>\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"2159\" data-end=\"2184\">29 anos</td>\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"2184\" data-end=\"2232\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">R$ 2.500</span></td>\n<td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-start=\"2232\" data-end=\"2286\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">R$ 2.000</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2 data-start=\"2288\" data-end=\"2343\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"importancia_de_o_segurado_manter_o_CNIS_atualizado\"></span>importância de o segurado manter o CNIS atualizado<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n<p data-start=\"2344\" data-end=\"2383\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Independentemente da aposentadoria estar próxima ou não, é recomendável revisar o CNIS periodicamente. Atualizações cadastrais, troca de atividade e novos vínculos podem deixar registros inconsistentes. Uma conferência anual ajuda a assegurar que sua trajetória contributiva esteja sendo bem acompanhada.</span></p>\n<h2 data-start=\"2385\" data-end=\"2399\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"conclusao\"></span>conclusão<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n<p data-start=\"2400\" data-end=\"2439\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">A revisão do CNIS — corrigindo vínculos e salários — é um direito valioso que pode resultar em benefícios mais justos e generosos. Embora burocrática, a ação tem impacto real no valor final da aposentadoria e demais benefícios do INSS. Seja administrativamente ou judicialmente, buscar o acerto do CNIS com atenção e documentação adequada é essencial para garantir que seu tempo de trabalho e contribuições sejam plenamente reconhecidos.</span></p>\n<h2 data-start=\"2441\" data-end=\"2465\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"perguntas_e_respostas\"></span>perguntas e respostas<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n<p data-start=\"2467\" data-end=\"2549\"><strong data-start=\"2467\" data-end=\"2507\">Como saber se meu CNIS está correto?</strong><br data-start=\"2507\" data-end=\"2510\" /><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Acesse o extrato pelo Meu INSS e compare com CTPS, holerites, GPS, IR, FGTS.</span></p>\n<p data-start=\"2551\" data-end=\"2691\"><strong data-start=\"2551\" data-end=\"2608\">Posso corrigir o CNIS mesmo sem ter pedido benefício?</strong><br data-start=\"2608\" data-end=\"2611\" /><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Sim — a correção independe de solicitação de benefício, conforme norma vigente</span> <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://desmistificando.com.br/como-corrigir-dados-no-cnis/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">ABL Advogados</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+12</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Desmistificando o Direito</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+12</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">ssantos.adv.br</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+12</span></span></span></a></span></span><span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://exame.com/brasil/guia-do-cidadao/como-corrigir-o-cnis-pela-internet-para-se-aposentar/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Exame</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+1</span></span></span></a></span></span><span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://lemosdemiranda.adv.br/cnis/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Lemos de Miranda</span></span></span></a></span></span><span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://abladvogados.com/artigos/acerto-de-vinculo-e-remuneracao/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">ABL Advogados</span></span></span></a></span></span><span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://lucastubino.adv.br/revisao-da-aposentadoria-por-erros-no-salario/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Serviços e Informações do Brasil</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+5</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">lucastubino.adv.br</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+5</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">rogeriograndino.com.br</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+5</span></span></span></a></span></span>.</p>\n<p data-start=\"2693\" data-end=\"2766\"><strong data-start=\"2693\" data-end=\"2724\">Qual o prazo para correção?</strong><br data-start=\"2724\" data-end=\"2727\" /><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Administrativamente, costuma ser 30 dias. Caso ultrapasse, pode-se recorrer via ação judicial ou mandado de segurança por demora excessiva.</span></p>\n<p data-start=\"2768\" data-end=\"2891\"><strong data-start=\"2768\" data-end=\"2808\">E depois da aposentadoria concedida?</strong><br data-start=\"2808\" data-end=\"2811\" /><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">É possível revisar dentro de 10 anos (decadência). Se comprovado erro, o benefício será recalculado e retroativos pagos</span> <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://lucastubino.adv.br/revisao-da-aposentadoria-por-erros-no-salario/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">lucastubino.adv.br</span></span></span></a></span></span>.</p>\n<p data-start=\"2893\" data-end=\"3054\"><strong data-start=\"2893\" data-end=\"2940\">Quando vale a pena buscar revisão judicial?</strong><br data-start=\"2940\" data-end=\"2943\" />Se o INSS negar acerto injustamente ou atrasar; ou em casos de urgência por idade, saúde ou valor comprometido.</p>\n<p data-start=\"3056\" data-end=\"3220\"><strong data-start=\"3056\" data-end=\"3106\">Contribuições de MEI aparecem automaticamente?</strong><br data-start=\"3106\" data-end=\"3109\" />Apenas se foram pagas corretamente e processadas. Se faltar, é possível comprovar via GPS e solicitar correção.</p>\n",
